          "text": "**Finding the 10th term and sum**\n\nThe user wants to determine the 10th term using the formula for pronic numbers, which is n(n+1). So, the 10th term is 10*11 = 110. \n\nNext, for the sum of the first 10 pronic numbers, I realize that it involves summing n(n+1) from 1 to 10. This gives the total of 440 through computation: the sum of squares and the sum of the first ten integers. \n\nSo ultimately, I conclude with the results: the 10th term is 110, and the sum is 440."
